## Summary

### Files Created
- **`schemas/chat.ts`** — Zod validation schemas for all chat types (ChatMessage, ProactiveMessage, ChatSnapshot, ContextSuggestion)
- **`services/proactiveMessageEngine.ts`** — Rule-based proactive message engine with 9 generators (vocabulary review, mistake review, weak skills, exam countdown, study streak, low activity, new content, daily plan, mistake pattern) + context suggestion generator
- **`utils/contextSuggestions.ts`** — Re-exports and helpers for context-aware suggestions
- **`components/ContextSuggestionCard.tsx`** — UI component for rendering context suggestions inline
- **`tests/proactiveMessageEngine.test.ts`** — 25 tests covering all rule generators and context suggestions
- **`tests/ChatWidget.test.tsx`** — 22 tests covering rendering, interactions, props, error states

### Files Modified
- **`services/messageStorage.ts`** — Added Zod validation on load, `exportToJson()` and `importFromJson()` methods, `getTotalInteractions()`
- **`types/index.ts`** — Added `className`, `contextSuggestions`, `onSendMessage`, `onQuickAction`, `onClearChat`, `title`, `subtitle`, `placeholder` to `ChatWidgetProps`
- **`hooks/useProactiveMessages.ts`** — Added `generateFromInput()` and `getContextSuggestionsForInput()` methods that delegate to the engine service
- **`components/ChatWidget.tsx`** — Added `onSendMessage` async callback (external AI), `onQuickAction` callback, `className` prop, error state display, disabled state during typing, extracted context suggestion rendering into `ContextSuggestionCard`
- **`index.ts`** — Added exports for new components/services/schemas

### Key Design Decisions
- **Separated concerns**: UI (`ChatWidget`) → hooks (`useProactiveMessages`) → service (`proactiveMessageEngine`) → schemas
- **Reusable callback pattern**: `onSendMessage` lets the parent handle AI responses; `onQuickAction` lets the parent intercept quick actions
